  <original-body>For latest edge Rails(Edge Rails revision       2463e38efd3cbcc10e7b0a93ad9c2d2224340668). When you generate model with &quot;script/generate model user&quot;
The file user_test.rb created in test/unit folder do not have line 
@@@ruby 
require File.dirname(__FILE__) + '/../test_helper'
@@@ in it. Instead it has
@@@ruby 
ruby 'test-helper'
@@@
which is wrong and so test fail until you make it correct.</original-body>
